Elvanie Nimbona (amụrụ ya na 15 Maachị 1998) bụ onye Burundi na-agba ọsọ ogologo. O sonyere na asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị ndị okenye na 2019 IAAF World Cross Country Championships. Ọ pụtara n'ọnọdụ nke iri ise na ise.
N'afọ 2017, o sonyere na asọmpi ụmụ nwanyị na afọ 2017 IAAF World Cross Country Championships nke emere na obodo Kampala, Uganda. Ọ pụtara n'ọnọdụ nke iri na isii.
N'afọ 2019, o mekwara asọmpi na igba ọsọ ụmụ nwanyị na 2019 World Athletics Championships nke emere na obodo Qatar a na-akpo Doha. Ọ gbachaghi ọsọ ya mgbe ahu.
